Hennessey Performance | Making Fast Cars Faster Since 1991
body: Hennessey Performance was founded more than 30 years ago and has been focused on pioneering automotive performance ever since. John Hennessey, our founder, and CEO made a name for himself in the early 1990s with race-winning vehicle modifications that gained global fame. Pursuing his true passion, John left his small environmental business and aimed his entrepreneurial skills at modifying, tuning, and enhancing high performance cars and trucks. Today, the company operates Hennessey Performance Engineering (HPE), Hennessey Special Vehicles (HSV), and the world-famous Tuner School where future vehicle engineers and tuners learn the trade. Hennessey has modified more than 10,000 cars and trucks since opening in 1991, and is h
ome to the largest lineup of late-model high-performance sports cars, muscle cars, supercars, trucks & SUVs, including the Venom F5 hypercar.

body: Super 3 continues a 113-year legacy of three-wheeled Morgan vehicles, introducing a new design language to the product range and continuing Morgan’s long tradition of doing things differently. From its mechanical underpinnings and design to its extensive options list and its name, everything about Super 3 is all-new.

Introducing the most dynamically capable Morgan ever produced. Addictive power, unrivalled exhilaration and a true drivers sports car, the all-new Morgan Plus Six represents a new era of performance and refinement for the Morgan range.

A number of exciting opportunities to experience Morgan are available to people of all ages. Based at the historic home of Morgan, Pickersleigh Road, our on-site Experience Centre offers a number of experience packages. From guided factory tours, hire cars, experience drives and afternoon tea, all of our individual experiences can be packaged together and enjoyed on your own, with family, friends or purchased as a gift voucher.

We are passionate about talking to our community, and our email bulletins will only ever contain the finest Morgan content, we would never send anything we wouldn’t want to receive ourselves.  Please enter your email address below if you would like to join our community and stay informed.

Hennessey Performance | Making Fast Cars Faster Since 1991
body: Hennessey Performance was founded more than 30 years ago and has been focused on pioneering automotive performance ever since. John Hennessey, our founder, and CEO made a name for himself in the early 1990s with race-winning vehicle modifications that gained global fame. Pursuing his true passion, John left his small environmental business and aimed his entrepreneurial skills at modifying, tuning, and enhancing high performance cars and trucks. Today, the company operates Hennessey Performance Engineering (HPE), Hennessey Special Vehicles (HSV), and the world-famous Tuner School where future vehicle engineers and tuners learn the trade. Hennessey has modified more than 10,000 cars and trucks since opening in 1991, and is h
ome to the largest lineup of late-model high-performance sports cars, muscle cars, supercars, trucks & SUVs, including the Venom F5 hypercar.

body: Super 3 continues a 113-year legacy of three-wheeled Morgan vehicles, introducing a new design language to the product range and continuing Morgan’s long tradition of doing things differently. From its mechanical underpinnings and design to its extensive options list and its name, everything about Super 3 is all-new.

Introducing the most dynamically capable Morgan ever produced. Addictive power, unrivalled exhilaration and a true drivers sports car, the all-new Morgan Plus Six represents a new era of performance and refinement for the Morgan range.

A number of exciting opportunities to experience Morgan are available to people of all ages. Based at the historic home of Morgan, Pickersleigh Road, our on-site Experience Centre offers a number of experience packages. From guided factory tours, hire cars, experience drives and afternoon tea, all of our individual experiences can be packaged together and enjoyed on your own, with family, friends or purchased as a gift voucher.

We are passionate about talking to our community, and our email bulletins will only ever contain the finest Morgan content, we would never send anything we wouldn’t want to receive ourselves.  Please enter your email address below if you would like to join our community and stay informed.

body: Hennessey Performance was founded more than 30 years ago and has been focused on pioneering automotive performance ever since. John Hennessey, our founder, and CEO made a name for himself in the early 1990s with race-winning vehicle modifications that gained global fame. Pursuing his true passion, John left his small environmental business and aimed his entrepreneurial skills at modifying, tuning, and enhancing high performance cars and trucks. Today, the company operates Hennessey Performance Engineering (HPE), Hennessey Special Vehicles (HSV), and the world-famous Tuner School where future vehicle engineers and tuners learn the trade. Hennessey has modified more than 10,000 cars and trucks since opening in 1991, and is h
ome to the largest lineup of late-model high-performance sports cars, muscle cars, supercars, trucks & SUVs, including the Venom F5 hypercar.

body: Super 3 continues a 113-year legacy of three-wheeled Morgan vehicles, introducing a new design language to the product range and continuing Morgan’s long tradition of doing things differently. Introducing the most dynamically capable Morgan ever produced. Addictive power, unrivalled exhilaration and a true drivers sports car, the all-new Morgan Plus Six represents a new era of performance and refinement for the Morgan range.

A number of exciting opportunities to experience Morgan are available to people of all ages. Based at the historic home of Morgan, Pickersleigh Road, our on-site Experience Centre offers a number of experience packages. From guided factory tours, hire cars, experience drives and afternoon tea, all of our individual experiences can be packaged together and enjoyed on your own, with family, friends or purchased as a gift voucher.
